Package at.peirleitner.core.util.local

Class GUI

java.lang.Object
at.peirleitner.core.util.local.GUI
All Implemented Interfaces:
org.bukkit.event.Listener
public class GUI
extends java.lang.Object
implements org.bukkit.event.Listener
This class represents a GUI that the User is able to interact with.
If the filled in Items exceed the Size of the Inventory you will also be able to navigate back and fourth between pages.
Since:
1.0.0
Author:
Markus Peirleitner (Rengobli)
